<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Order Success</title>
    <style>
        body { text-align: center; padding: 50px; font-family: sans-serif; }
        .success-icon { font-size: 80px; color: #28a745; }
        .btn-home { display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px; padding: 10px 20px; background: #007bff; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="success-icon">✔</div>
    <h1>Order Placed Successfully!</h1>
    <p>Thank you for shopping with <strong><%= storeName %></strong>.</p>
    <p>Your inventory has been updated, and your items are being prepared for shipping.</p>
    
    <a href="/" class="btn-home">Continue Shopping</a>
</body>
</html>